text: Hasab Al-Rasoul Marhum Bakheit () known by his nickname Hasabu Al-Kabeer () (years 1940s – June 24, 2011 in Khartoum) is a former international Sudanese footballer who played with Burri SC. ==Achievements== *Sudan Premier League :Champions (1): 1969 ==External links== *حسبو الكبير - alsahafa.sd Category:2011 deaths Category:Sudanese footballers Category:Sudan international footballers Category:Association footballers not categorized by position Category:Year of birth missing
